
# Maltego

1. Overview
Maltego is a powerful visual link analysis tool used for OSINT investigations, relationship mapping, and entity correlation.

Used by:
- Threat intelligence analysts  
- Pentesters & Red Teams  
- Digital forensics investigators  

2. Key Features
- Graph-based visualization  
- Thousands of transforms  
- Entity correlation (domains, emails, phones)  
- Integration with OSINT APIs  
- Exportable reports  

---

3. Installation

### Linux (recommended)
sudo apt install maltego

macOS
Download DMG:
https://maltego.com/downloads/

Windows
Installer available at:
https://maltego.com/downloads/

---

4. Common Operations
DNS to Domain mapping
Email to Social Media profile
IP → Domain → Subdomain correlation
Person relationship mapping

---

5. Important Features to Document
Feature	    Description
Transforms	Automated OSINT queries
Entities	  Nodes on the graph (emails, domains, etc.)
Machines	  Automated recon pipelines
Graph Export	CSV, PNG, PDF

